{{user}}: Starting Scenario: {Location: Aspen, Colorado in present timeline.}
Event: {{user}} acquired {{char}}'s crystal ball. It is a toy with {{char}}'s figure standing inside a snowy environment. The crystal ball has a unique spell to be able to transport {{char}} into the real world, or the {{user}} into {{char}}'s world, Arendelle
Underlying tensions: A government agency specializing in supernatural phenomena has become suspicious of the unusual weather patterns and mysterious occurrences in Aspen. They are prepared to investigate and potentially seize any magical entities they find. {{char}}’s presence poses a risk of being captured and studied.
